(1789, 'Robotan', 'Unknown', 'Kids', 'Comedy', 'Unknown', 6.18, '1966', 'Based on a manga by Morita Kenji.\n\nHousehold robot Robotan, made by a nerdy school boy named Kan-chan, lives with an everyday Japanese family as a domestic servant and friend to the children.\n\n(Source: AniDB)\n\n\n\n\n\nStudioUnknown\n\nSource\n\nDemographicKids', 'Kids', 'Finished', 104, 25, 485, NULL),
