(1793, '47 Todoufuken', 'Pollyanna Graphics', 'Kids', 'Comedy', 'Original', 5.51, '2011', '\"47 Prefecture Dogs\" is a short flash animation from a voice over variety TV program in Japan called \"SAY! YOU! SAY! ME!\" The animation takes Japan\'s 47 prefectures—or more specifically, the local delicacies or famous landmarks from each of the regions—an', 'Kids', 'Finished', 26, 1, 466, NULL),
